title: 이달의소녀탐구 #372 (LOONA TV #372)
summary:
The Second Day of Line&Up. OEC arrive in casual clothes.
0:01 -- Olivia Hye misplaces her in-ear and it could have been a disaster. However, she finds it soon enough.
0:21 -- "This is MC Yves~! It will be much better twoday as it is the second day! Fighting!!"
0:31 -- YeoJin singining 'Rosy'. It slowly turns into an ASMR session.
JinSoul: “But of course I did well. Today I have more time to make it more enjoyable!”; OEC: “Fighting~ Fralalala~”
0:42 -- Pan to OEC. Everyone feels much relaxed on the second day. They all take pictures including the iconic OT12.
